727067f-a.text:
1)  Jamaica Avenue, at the N.E. corner of 173rd Street, showing Judge R. Busteed's House, once owned by J. Vanderveer.  Bob Rodman also lived here.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
March, 1923

2)  The same house, years later.  The exterior has been stuccoed and other alterations made.

P.L. Sperr
March 25, 1932
